Text.Page:
We're encountering heavier than anticipated resistance, so we're dispatching you.

Engage the naga survivors guarding the Chamber of Lost Souls, including {@LinkCreature:42#610#skeletal guardians}, {@LinkCreature:42#200#Dagonite slayers}, {@LinkCreature:42#300#naga fighters}, {@LinkCreature:42#700#vicious bone imps}, and {@LinkCreature:42#800#besharan traffickers}.

Report your progress to Glasrinne in Frontera.
The nagas are weaker, thanks to you. But there's still a lot to do, and I hope you'll stick around to help out.
I never said it'd be easy, but what you're doing is helping us stay alive and do what we came here to do. Don't stop now.
